{"tid":1584482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[關公工程] 有冇人覺得重建連儂牆之前可以做一件事先？","createTime":"2019-09-21T06:39:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T01:27:34.000Z","uid":60583,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5fd841db722a1b5b3c67a439e96e20bef78db3f5","tid":1584482,"uid":60583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T06:39:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">就係「清潔香港」！</div></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n今日眼見一批冷血人士（未知是否香港人）係全港18區製造大量垃圾<br />\n<br />\n有圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1H6emL0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1H6emL0.png&h=ba91def2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片來自立場新聞Facebook<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VNfVQEn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNfVQEn.png&h=e05766ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片轉自毛EE Facebook<br />\n<br />\n成地都係雜物，破壞巿容之餘，更加有礙行人，好憂心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n何律師發起嘅「清潔香港」行動好值得我地學習<br />\n有冇人覺得我地可以咁做:<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 影低今日各處嘅垃圾，同製造垃圾嘅人，你可以同佢講想表揚佢地幫佢地影翻張相</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">2. 大肆宣傳聽日將會搞一個「真。清潔香港」</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">3. 聽日清理地上垃圾嘅時候叫晒大量傳媒過來影相拍片，比全球見到黑衣香港人=好人，大媽大叔= _ _ _</span><br />\n<br />\n係好和理非，但公關就正正係和理非要做嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aaed273fe85eb00d69e17c5654760df405080af","tid":1584482,"uid":60583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T06:39:26.000Z","msg":"堆1"},{"pid":"9ccccb6964e9f366901db1628b82da3c97320379","tid":1584482,"uid":60583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T06:39:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f4481f592eaf03cad43cd887b74eabd0339476af","tid":1584482,"uid":60583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T06:39:47.000Z","msg":"堆2"},{"pid"